會嘅記錄 （ <a href=\"https://www.congress.gov/bill/116th-congress/house-bill/3289/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.congress.gov%2Fbill%2F116th-congress%2Fhouse-bill%2F3289%2F&d=sTs6EBDlf0QtlDbt2wLSRnlPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=5d32ef6f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.congress.gov/bill/116th-congress/house-bill/3289/</a> ）<br />\n呢條 Hong Kong Human Rights and Democracy Act 2019<br />\n喺 今年6月13日提出後<br />\n暫時無任何進度<br />\n與其大家响度討論<br />\n不如去游說侵侵同班美國國會議員咪仲好<br />\n<br />\n由於侵侵好容易先入為主<br />\n大家不妨同佢講多啲<br />\n諸如香港係中國經濟嘅春袋嘅理據<br />\n咁佢或者會覺得加快推動條《香港人權及民主法案》<br />\n會成為佢對大陸貿易戰嘅核彈都唔定"},{"pid":"6b9edf9319b0dfca29c259306c0fcdaf842426cf","tid":1515130,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T04:50:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cicFax7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcicFax7.png&h=ca9eff31&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NJ6FUZO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNJ6FUZO.png&h=a8c6ffd7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a0499d96d090f6b1bb1242e6540af2f65eda8077","tid":1515130,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b9edf9319b0dfca29c259306c0fcdaf842426cf","tid":1515130,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T04:50:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cicFax7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcicFax7.png&h=ca9eff31&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NJ6FUZO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNJ6FUZO.png&h=a8c6ffd7&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T04:57:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{